Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.81,0:00:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 不要回頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.73,0:00:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 邁步出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.90,0:00:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼淚是閃閃發光的勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.90,0:00:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一步 都化為甘霖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.88,0:00:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight Fight 更加自信了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.41,0:00:36.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要的東西就捨去 這樣也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.50,0:00:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在無限廣闊的心中蔓延開來喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.78,0:00:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於受傷時刻之外　看不見的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.83,0:00:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若現在開始映入雙眸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.78,0:00:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just Try-again
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.11,0:01:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變得強大 抓住機會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.10,0:01:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 無論何時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.11,0:01:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 都要堅信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.14,0:01:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢想絕對能實現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.23,0:01:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有多遙遠 都不害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.23,0:01:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight Fight 更能感覺到明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.09,0:01:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫戰部渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.60,0:01:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了打倒支配了在遙遠天空上的星界山的多壞達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.47,0:01:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們以第七星界為目標展開了冒險旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.70,0:01:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了得到神聖松明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.08,0:01:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從第五星界來到聖天界的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.64,0:01:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裏要各自尋找自己的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.49,0:01:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到了麾沙村的火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.36,0:01:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮地得到了愛的證明的心形標記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.22,0:02:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也會是"超"有趣又有型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.09,0:02:08.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三十三話\N在海洋發現的真實之愛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.81,0:02:22.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛愛愛…找到了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.57,0:02:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到了愛啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.05,0:02:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「愛…愛…」的,真吵的家夥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.22,0:02:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子,你是怎樣找到愛的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.52,0:02:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛?這個標記叫做愛嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.43,0:02:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了令第五星界恢複原狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.67,0:02:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也要找到那心形標記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.03,0:02:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子,你是怎樣找到那愛的?請告訴我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.48,0:03:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛的形態是千變萬化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.31,0:03:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並不是可以問人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.32,0:03:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加麾斯利路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.64,0:03:07.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小加麾…這是我的愛嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.78,0:03:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.36,0:03:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子很漂亮的找到自己的愛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.33,0:03:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了,下一個是誰好呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.84,0:03:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子就你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.21,0:03:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去把愛找回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.26,0:03:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.29,0:03:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了,快點去吧,海火子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.84,0:03:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找你自己的愛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.29,0:03:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子,拜託你了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.93,0:03:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有時會有點魯莽,要保持平常心啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.03,0:03:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武一郎老師說得對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.15,0:03:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要太勉強啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.17,0:03:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知什麼愛還是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.94,0:03:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我立刻會找出來的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.21,0:04:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奮鬥,火子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.78,0:04:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好,我去了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.65,0:04:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜了,火子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.49,0:04:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼人?不要躲起來了快出來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.47,0:04:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.94,0:04:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底想去哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.65,0:04:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪…哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.68,0:04:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你連自己的愛在哪裏也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.58,0:04:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.92,0:04:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.63,0:04:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事我想也沒想過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.23,0:04:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,餵,加麾斯利路!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.71,0:04:59.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那東西還給我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.00,0:05:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那個裏面有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.47,0:05:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有你的父親被封印著,是這樣吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.64,0:05:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為…為什麼你會知!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.31,0:05:10.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想我把父親還給你的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.27,0:05:12.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便從我的手上跳上來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.41,0:05:14.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你真的愛你的父親的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.68,0:05:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該可以跳到這光球那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.11,0:05:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡,竟戲弄人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.15,0:05:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看著吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.69,0:05:27.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.47,0:05:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的感情稍微有一點模湖不清
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.77,0:05:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.46,0:05:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你的心底裏有某件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.77,0:05:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令你不能深信你的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.28,0:05:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的父親是個沒出色的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.92,0:05:52.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯,沒錯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.75,0:05:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的父親是個沒出色的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.69,0:05:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯,沒錯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.90,0:06:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.74,0:06:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.81,0:06:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏不是我出身的麾利多村嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.45,0:06:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我成長的家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.80,0:06:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽…媽媽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.82,0:06:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸…爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.41,0:06:50.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轍美!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.31,0:06:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轍美…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.55,0:06:54.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.90,0:06:57.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才吃下的藥已生效了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.82,0:07:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是,這樣下去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.25,0:07:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的太太和肚內孩子能否得救也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.19,0:07:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚內的孩子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.70,0:07:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道,我回到了我自己出世之前的時空嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.97,0:07:16.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漁火,你去哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.74,0:07:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難…難道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.91,0:07:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去捉依沙拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.21,0:07:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.01,0:07:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依…依沙拿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.63,0:07:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依沙拿是傳說中的魚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.11,0:07:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然說它的肉能給吃了的人得到想像不到的生命力…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.39,0:07:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前村裏的人想去捕捉依沙拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.86,0:07:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是,和那巨大的依沙拿做對手的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.93,0:07:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部失去了性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.47,0:07:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漁火,不吉利的事我不說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.35,0:07:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要對依沙拿出手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.24,0:07:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許會沒命啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.92,0:08:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不,我要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.07,0:08:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是,我知道答案了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.83,0:08:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的爸爸是個沒出色的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.75,0:08:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯,沒錯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.47,0:08:25.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的父親是個沒出色的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.30,0:08:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯,沒錯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.47,0:08:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.53,0:08:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的爸爸是村中第一的勇士!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.75,0:08:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是沒出色的父親!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.01,0:08:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.49,0:08:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的父親捉不到依沙拿回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.68,0:08:40.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是個沒出色的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.83,0:08:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親始終捉不到依沙拿回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.79,0:08:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽像快死般把我生了出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.21,0:08:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後我便被說是捉不了依沙拿的沒出色父親的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.53,0:08:55.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天被人取笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.01,0:08:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.17,0:09:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼爸爸不把依沙拿捉回來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.43,0:09:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底為什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.56,0:09:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加麾斯利路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.91,0:09:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的父親在海中見到了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.35,0:09:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒一個知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.83,0:09:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有一件事可以證實的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.22,0:09:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那問題令你對父親的愛出現陰雲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.97,0:09:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漁火,不要出海啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.21,0:09:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊,要捉依沙拿是沒可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.11,0:09:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你絕對會被殺的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.44,0:09:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不論你們怎樣說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.86,0:09:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要捉依沙拿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.07,0:09:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是,漁火…誰替你撐船?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.47,0:09:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一個人不可能捕魚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.59,0:09:50.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我替你撐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.76,0:09:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.74,0:09:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在村中沒見過的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.20,0:09:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎?小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.67,0:10:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯,我對撐船很有自信的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.91,0:10:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.01,0:10:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了,小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.53,0:10:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.15,0:10:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不加油的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.58,0:10:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚內的孩子也完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.21,0:10:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸在海裏見到了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.68,0:10:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要用這雙眼確認一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.17,0:11:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轍美!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.51,0:11:16.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油,加油啊!轍美!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.27,0:11:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.59,0:12:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.77,0:12:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了把我訓練成才的爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.97,0:12:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我非常嚴格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.52,0:12:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子,你不能鬆懈的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.99,0:12:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.86,0:12:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公,請你停手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.26,0:12:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說謊是不能成為男子漢的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.20,0:12:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子也明白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.26,0:12:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你原諒他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.01,0:12:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然這樣,爸爸卻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.54,0:12:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸卻還是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.87,0:13:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸卻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.26,0:13:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.50,0:13:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.65,0:13:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依沙拿來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.77,0:13:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好掌舵啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.07,0:13:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那便是依沙拿…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.37,0:14:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.18,0:14:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好站起來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.98,0:14:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.55,0:14:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它很懂得優勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.13,0:14:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它知道這樣的船可以用波浪擊破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.73,0:14:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了,他又再從側邊來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.53,0:14:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次都是拍打側邊太危險了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.73,0:14:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.67,0:14:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣啊?大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.97,0:14:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有本事呢,小孩!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.85,0:14:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.87,0:15:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.21,0:15:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸…爸爸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.20,0:15:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸…爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.23,0:15:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有這個可能的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.80,0:15:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼不浮上來啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.28,0:15:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難…難道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.45,0:15:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.29,0:15:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畜生!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.36,0:16:00.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我來收拾你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.84,0:16:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼家夥,我站不起來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.90,0:16:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能像爸爸一樣跳進去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.80,0:16:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這混帳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.34,0:16:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這家夥怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.97,0:16:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來了結你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.82,0:16:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要收拾你救媽媽!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.29,0:17:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.59,0:17:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔,我很擔心你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.17,0:17:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看,這家夥雖然不知是什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.79,0:17:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躺下了動不了,要出手便是時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.50,0:17:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩,不能殺依沙拿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.34,0:17:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以殺依沙拿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.77,0:17:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.95,0:17:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.17,0:17:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這機會不會有第二次的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.60,0:17:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才飛身去刺依沙拿的你,去了哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.69,0:17:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的膽小病又發作了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.19,0:17:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是這麼沒志氣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.60,0:17:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.17,0:17:48.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你要放棄啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.70,0:17:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要幹!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.35,0:18:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸…爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.82,0:18:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以殺依沙拿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.04,0:18:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看看那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.68,0:18:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是依沙拿的嬰孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.85,0:18:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我的妻子為成為母親在痛苦著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.26,0:18:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那依沙拿也是母親,同樣是母親我殺不了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.88,0:19:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是生命的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.05,0:19:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命的…力量?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.05,0:19:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼細小的軀體也努力地在生存著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.79,0:19:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這便是生命的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.03,0:19:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也相信我妻子和孩子的生命力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.76,0:19:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要在這裏分別了,大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.50,0:19:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.60,0:20:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來,我還沒問你的名字呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.20,0:20:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我嗎?我叫…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.90,0:20:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫海火子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.97,0:20:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.69,0:20:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔,好名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.55,0:20:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得你關照了,海火子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.67,0:20:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子出世的話,要好好疼愛他啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.15,0:20:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.96,0:20:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.02,0:20:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西是…我的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.06,0:21:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.11,0:21:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做得很好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.62,0:21:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個很健康的男孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.53,0:21:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.65,0:21:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轍美,做得很好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.15,0:21:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了一個很不可思議的夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.93,0:21:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.96,0:21:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你和孩子一起去捕魚的夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.53,0:21:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和這孩子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.54,0:21:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漁火,你要替這孩子起什麼名字?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.27,0:21:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子的名字是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.84,0:21:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子…是海火子啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.10,0:21:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.51,0:21:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對,是海火子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.10,0:21:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好名字呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.95,0:22:02.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.52,0:22:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要長大成才啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.29,0:22:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在 陰霾的天空裏烏雲漸漸散去 陽光透過雲層照了下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.86,0:22:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個人仰望這天空的哪個角落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.98,0:22:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眩目的彩虹 即將出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.71,0:22:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注定出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.53,0:22:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧 奔跑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.16,0:23:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁著光線還沒有消失的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.59,0:23:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待著明天的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.74,0:23:12.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧 奔跑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.32,0:23:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熠熠生輝的彩虹彼岸裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.73,0:23:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吹出了兩個人未來的風
